rows.label: fev11_530_175_msg0001
rows.name:
Right, all. Ready for a quick mosey
across the desert?

rows.label: fev11_530_175_msg0002
rows.name:
That is, assuming you've all got your
medicine?

rows.label: fev11_530_175_msg0006
rows.name:
We're all good! I've been keeping
tabs on him since morning.

rows.label: fev11_530_175_msg0007
rows.name:
Then let's embrace the arid beauty
of the Dannagh Desert. We'll be able
to see the capital before long!

rows.label: fev11_530_175_msg0008
rows.name: I hope we won't get lost out there.

rows.label: fev11_530_175_msg0009
rows.name:
We don't have the luxury. The capital
needs to be informed of Metsu's
intentions as soon as possible.
